    BasicCrossoverModule, MyOperatorModule

    public abstract class CrossoverModule
extends OperatorModule<Crossover<?>>
    The CrossoverModule is used for modules for the Crossover operator. A new Crossover operator can be registered by implementing this module and adding the operator with OperatorModule.addOperator(java.lang.Class<? extends P>).
